Reylene Pearce https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reylene_Pearce 0 Reylene Pearce is an Australian actress, best known for her long-running role in the television drama series Prisoner as Phyllis Hunt. She appeared in the show from 1979 to 1984, during which time the role had developed from a background bit part to a central character. She appeared in an Australian independent film "Moonlight Magic" (2007) as Delilah, a breast cancer survivor.
